    <item>
      <title>迪士尼乐园业务放缓抵消流媒体利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/disney-s-parks-slowdown-offset-streaming-profit-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，华特迪士尼公布了第三季度业绩，业绩喜忧参半，其著名主题公园的疲软抵消了流媒体业务的首次盈利。Lightshed 合伙人 Rich Greenfield 与 Ed Ludlow 一起在“彭博科技”节目中讨论该公司的流媒体业务。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/disney-s-parks-slowdown-offset-streaming-profit-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:15:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷讨论通过桑坦德银行筹集 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/argentina-said-to-discuss-raising-1-billion-through-santander</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿根廷政府正在与桑坦德银行就一笔 10 亿美元贷款进行谈判，这是总统哈维尔·米莱伊 (Javier Milei) 在 1 月份偿还债务之前确保现金的举措之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/argentina-said-to-discuss-raising-1-billion-through-santander</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:13:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Shopify 总裁谈业绩和股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/shopify-president-on-results-shares-rising-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Shopify 公布第二季度销售额和利润超过分析师预期后股价飙升，表明这家加拿大电子商务公司正在设法应对谨慎的消费者支出。Shopify 总裁 Harley Finkelstein 与 Ed Ludlow 一起在“彭博科技”上讨论业绩。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/shopify-president-on-results-shares-rising-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:10:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Reddit 首席运营官谈销售预测和 AI Play</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/reddit-coo-on-sales-forecast-ai-play-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Reddit 表示，预计新的数据授权合作伙伴关系和广告技术将带来稳定的收入增长，为新上市公司的未来发展指明了方向。Reddit 首席运营官 Jen Wong 与 Ed Ludlow 一起在“彭博科技”上讨论业绩。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/reddit-coo-on-sales-forecast-ai-play-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:06:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
