      <title>经济观点波动导致市政债券遭遇近一年来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/munis-see-biggest-rout-in-nearly-a-year-as-economic-views-swing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于固定收益市场的投资者减少对优质债券的投资，市政债券周三下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/munis-see-biggest-rout-in-nearly-a-year-as-economic-views-swing</guid>
